text: Sturla Snær Snorrason (born 1 March 1994) is an Icelandic alpine skier. He competed in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Alpine skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Icelandic male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Iceland
